00:00:17.430 --> 00:00:21.018
What are you preparing today?
Methi Muthiya

00:00:23.711 --> 00:00:25.448
Ingredients required to prepare Methi Muthiya :

00:00:25.768 --> 00:00:29.142
Gram flour, Fenugreek leaves, Coriander leaves, Cumin seeds,
Mustard seeds

00:00:29.501 --> 00:00:32.703
Carom seeds (Ajwain), Cooking Soda, Aji-No-Moto, Garam Masala

00:00:33.077 --> 00:00:35.725
Grated Coconut, Chat Masala, Red Chilli powder, Oil

00:00:43.973 --> 00:00:45.552
Take 1 cup Gram flour in a bowl.

00:00:51.809 --> 00:00:54.920
Add the Fenugreek leaves.

00:01:10.315 --> 00:01:12.195
Add 1 tbsp Carom seeds-Cumin seeds powder.
Note : Equal quantities of Carom seeds &amp; Cumin seeds to be powdered together.

00:01:20.111 --> 00:01:24.620
Add a pinch of Cooking Soda.
Add Red Chilli powder &amp; Salt to taste.

00:01:29.285 --> 00:01:30.683
Add a pinch of Aji-no-Moto.

00:01:35.810 --> 00:01:37.650
Add sufficient water to make a dough.

00:01:44.379 --> 00:01:46.665
Divide this dough into small &amp; equal portions.

00:01:57.282 --> 00:01:59.538
Heat water in a pan.

00:02:07.155 --> 00:02:09.462
Make rolls with the dough.

00:02:11.887 --> 00:02:14.323
Steam cook these rolls.

00:02:34.828 --> 00:02:36.888
Once cooked, shift the rolls to a bowl.

00:02:48.285 --> 00:02:50.518
Cut these Methi Muthiya to small pieces with a knife.

00:02:56.743 --> 00:02:58.354
Heat Oil in a pan.

00:03:03.374 --> 00:03:05.586
Add Cumin seeds &amp; Fenugreek leaves.

00:03:15.439 --> 00:03:17.394
Add the cooked Methi Muthiya.

00:03:20.657 --> 00:03:21.978
Add Salt to taste.

00:03:23.839 --> 00:03:24.939
Add Red Chilli powder.

00:03:26.330 --> 00:03:27.622
Add Garam Masala.

00:03:41.658 --> 00:03:42.935
Add Curry leaves.

00:03:52.332 --> 00:03:54.844
Add the grated Coconut powder.

00:04:16.227 --> 00:04:18.548
Shift the contents to a serving bowl.

00:04:24.326 --> 00:04:26.540
Sprinkle 1 tsp Lemon juice.

00:04:29.564 --> 00:04:31.369
Garnish with Coriander leaves.

00:04:33.110 --> 00:04:34.944
Serve with Tomato Ketchup.

